title: Tilly's Travis Barker Signing
description: Recently, Famous Stars & Straps founder, Blink 182 drummer and Psycho White kingpin Travis Barker returned to his hometown of Riverside, California and paid a visit to Tilly's Galleria At Tyler. Check what happened when Travis rolled through in his custom Coupe de Ville with a handful of Famous family members including, Manny Santiago, Felix Arguelles and Kurtis Colamonico. Fans went crazy, Travis signed anything and everything and made history with this epic in-store Tilly's signing. Go to Tillys.com for the newest Famous Stars & Straps and Psycho White goods.
